  '\uD83D\uDCC5 OI: $' + (oi ? (oi/1e6).toFixed(1) + 'B' : 'N/A') + '   ETH: <b>$' + Math.round(ethP) + '</b> (' + fmtPct(ethChg) + ' 24H) ' + ethConfirm,
